1) run the ansible setup script
ansible_setup.sh


2) configure CIS hardening
cis_bash.sh

3) install dependencies (reboot need it after this)
k8s_dependencies_all.sh             # on all nodes
k8s_dependencies_master.sh          # only on the master nodes


4) init master, playbook to start the init control-plane (ONLY FOR THE INIT CLUSTER STRAT)
k8s_init_master.sh

5) configure more control plane
k8s_master.sh


6) configure more worker
